{"tid":1069211,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一個月三次扁桃腺發炎點算？","createTime":"2019-03-19T21:07:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-19T23:42:22.000Z","uid":190211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4468fab3b09b0be7de6fe6d1247bfece15447567","tid":1069211,"uid":190211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T21:07:18.000Z","msg":"一開始係左邊發現有扁桃腺發炎 好痛痛到連食嘢都食唔到 之後去咗醫生度開藥 食咗10日antibiotics 食完之後好返 五日後就到右邊扁桃腺發炎 醫生今次開咗七日antibiotics 上星期五食晒成個療程 今朝發現右邊又開始有白色珍珠... 我應該點算？ 利申係加拿大"},{"pid":"e94a032d35c814e2206b23240431b461c0cc2b13","tid":1069211,"uid":43704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T22:27:15.000Z","msg":"用棉花棒細細力清出黎<br />\n平時早晚用漱口水清一清喉嚨<br />\n睇醫生要食曬一個療程嘅抗生素<br />\n以後注意飲食 無食太多熱氣野"},{"pid":"797752615e9ee24f6fd1e5eb9ef04d5c53cc4a84","tid":1069211,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T22:40:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />樓主下世小心啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61eb03264a76bf73d952e52f578947a22fbbd9b6","tid":1069211,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T22:42:13.000Z","msg":"割"},{"pid":"0d0bc2184b9cb4701c268a84ebd90864c42eda90","tid":1069211,"uid":242702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T23:19:46.000Z","msg":"真係要注意飲食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你識唔識煲下粥呀 發緊炎盡量都食下嘢 流質最好 因為其實只會食緊都痛到你想喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n良好習慣同口腔衛生都好重要 都係早睡早起嗰啲老套嘢啦 口腔衛生就....幫人用口時清潔左先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71d06a9cd1279b134fb089b09227c46e86b971ed","tid":1069211,"uid":242702,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"61eb03264a76bf73d952e52f578947a22fbbd9b6","tid":1069211,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T22:42:13.000Z","msg":"割"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201